    "2 Evaluating General-Purpose Technologies: the LLM",
    "Why might we be willing to directly plug LLM outputs into our empirical studies?",
    "For two reasons.",
    "The first relates to the impressive performance of LLMs on benchmark evaluations, combined with memorable examples of their capabilities.",
    "The second is our tendency to draw inferences and generalize from how LLMs performed on some tasks to how they are likely to perform on other tasks."
